text: France Aviation Civile Services, previously DSNA Services,‘DSNA SERVICES’ DEVIENT ‘FRANCE AVIATION CIVILE SERVICES’ is a consulting company,FRANCE AVIATION CIVILE SERVICES (FRACS) started by the DGAC and the ENAC in 2013. It gives to clients the expertise of French civil aviation in regulation, security and air navigation. Its President is Mr Farid Zizi, previous President of the ICAO Air Navigation Commission.Farid Zizi, de l’OACI à DSNA Services ==References== == Further reading == * Category:Aviation in France Category:French Civil Aviation University Category:1981 establishments in Europe Category:1980s establishments in France
